snippet.title: Bubsy: Paws on Fire! Pre-Order Teaser
snippet.description:
Bubsy is back! More characters, more moves and over 100 levels in his greatest adventure yet! Check out Bubsy: Paws on Fire! on Amazon now!!!

Pre-order here:
https://www.amazon.com/stores/node/5549660011

Sign up for the Bubsy fan club at
bubsy.com
